reviewText: Expect me to boost it to 5 stars once I get baptized in the Holy Spirit and speak in tongues. But it sure felt like my brain was about to explode, and I think I felt something in my body too!

This DVD and CD set inspires Holy Spirit baptized believers in Jesus Christ to USE the gift God has given them for all the reasons, both personal and in ministry to others, it is meant for. Use it often and for its greatest purposes. Be inspired, like I was, to reignite God's available power in your life and for the lives of others.
